WingRazor walked out carefully and looked at the maximal before her. 
His over all appearance was prebio dated... He was all metal and 
seemed strange some how, but she shook off the feelings, and turned 
to the cockpit. "My commander is uncontious, he has a head injury and 
our medic is still in his stasis pod..."

Rave flew in overhead his frame casting a large shadow. "Howdy down 
there... Rave.... MAXIMIZE!" He landed with a thump as he smiled and 
turned to WingRazor. "The med labs smashed, no help there."
